{"tid":1588482,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"熱門算法是否有漏洞？","createTime":"2019-09-22T23:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T09:12:31.000Z","uid":58762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa266f238c917af06144a5a6d46edbff4a1c7a3","tid":1588482,"uid":58762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T23:55:48.000Z","msg":"大面IU心情勁靚！狂派飛吻！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588457</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個 post 只係樓主一個人短時間內貼大量圖，就直上熱門第一，係咪算法出咗漏洞？"},{"pid":"20139c994dacdca48fd260355cbb7cf746aa07db","tid":1588482,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T23:57:42.000Z","msg":"是"},{"pid":"b144912b316fe4290d9dfed705234e31107ac8b2","tid":1588482,"uid":9315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:56:37.000Z","msg":"應該係好多會員追蹤緊樓主  佢開post就即刻多人入去睇姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用Click rate set熱門都好正路<br />\n與其問點解行動post難推  不如問下係咪少咗人click入行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28735218489c1cbe2532f3000ea0602523259885","tid":1588482,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20139c994dacdca48fd260355cbb7cf746aa07db","tid":1588482,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T23:57:42.000Z","msg":"是"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:12:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">熱門台準則</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D95EEK3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD95EEK3.png&h=f459d2f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日新增納入「不推文回覆」為其中一項上到熱門嘅因素<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnjjweZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmnjjweZ.png&h=51886a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>目前已知熱門分數計算有以下數項：<br />\n1. 瀏覽人次 (分數佔最高比重)<br />\n2. 瀏覽時間<br />\n3. 正負皮數量 (分數佔最低比重)<br />\n4. 發表時間<br />\n5. 不推文回覆 (分數比重不明)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n熱門系統亦會自動<span style=\"color: red;\">依據分台避免熱門內容種類過於單一</span>。<br />\n換言之，應該點都會是旦塞幾個台較為多人睇嘅 post 上熱門。<br />\n避免熱門內容過於單一 (淨得時事台 POST)"}]}